title: Ep. 109 - Kavanaugh Accusations Flimsy, Michael Avenatti and Media Malpractice
description:
Democrats have conjured up some more accusations against Brett Kavanaugh. These accusations are the flimsiest yet. Let's talk about why the new allegations are not credible, and why Republicans need to put an end to this and just confirm Kavanaugh.
